data.meta_description: Explore our range of estates for your new home with Domaine Homes. Find your perfect location. Browse estates now!
data.text:
High Grove is located in the heart of North West Sydney, offers convenience in the form of amenities, transport options and schools for families and professionals alike - perfect for achieving maximum property growth. Located in the heart of North West Sydney,

Discover your brand-new home at Fairwood Rise, Rouse Hill. With affordable house and land packages, we take the stress out of buying and building.

Escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life, whilst still being in the heart of North West Sydney in this brand-new community. Even better, in your brand-new home! Discover our Oakville packages.

Anambah Rise is conveniently situated in one of Newcastle’s fastest growing regions, with a wide range of retail, commercial and community spaces within close reach. Just minutes from the nearest shops and services, it’s a perfect start for first home buyers and growing families!

Nestled within the Calderwood Valley Estate, an idyllic place to build your forever home and create lasting memories, surrounded by breathtaking natural beauty. At Calderwood, you’ll discover a well-rounded lifestyle with excellent schools and a variety of lifestyle destinations, all within easy reach. There’s always something to explore and enjoy!
